{"tid":2133172,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"豪宅天璽首次出現肺炎確診個案！36歲男患者中招！","createTime":"2020-07-31T01:55:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-31T09:39:29.000Z","uid":79563,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7c93c720937a7b46916bf76c02b2df39ec21c13e","tid":2133172,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T01:55:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/觀塘多18人確診屯門添11宗-天璽上榜慈雲山僅1宗-005600268.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%E8%A7%80%E5%A1%98%E5%A4%9A18%E4%BA%BA%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E6%B7%BB11%E5%AE%97-%E5%A4%A9%E7%92%BD%E4%B8%8A%E6%A6%9C%E6%85%88%E9%9B%B2%E5%B1%B1%E5%83%851%E5%AE%97-005600268.html&d=LJfbHi1nzQR09hbgKwAG14Znnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=168161f0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/觀塘多18人確診屯門添11宗-天璽上榜慈雲山僅1宗-005600268.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/nN1XeXw33Y97d8ggNNQUAA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20200731a085654.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FnN1XeXw33Y97d8ggNNQUAA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20200731a085654.jpg&h=18ee38b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】政府昨日（30日）公布本港新增149宗新冠肺炎確診個案，連續9日感染宗數突破3位數，且單日確診數字再創新高。衛生署衛生防護中心資料顯示，觀塘大增18宗個案，對入的將軍澳和西貢共多7宗，屯門有11名居民染疫。<br />\n<br />\n其中，觀塘順利紀律部隊宿舍有3人受感染，觀塘寶珮苑寶珊閣多3宗，屯門兆康苑兆基閣有4名居民確診。<br />\n<br />\n位於九龍站上蓋的豪宅天璽，住有一名36歲男患者，大角嘴港灣豪庭、灣仔尚翹峰、觀塘麗港城、荃灣朗逸峯麗港城亦有居民中招。而根據最新數字，之前大爆發的慈雲山靜下來，只有慈樂邨樂旺樓1宗個案。"},{"pid":"249a7035b4d74da0c4815eb9ff5b5322d5ce5a35","tid":2133172,"uid":346701,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T02:06:31.000Z","msg":"九成九賀回歸群組延伸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"422662c4871f68367fc52420be6b33bfdcf7899c","tid":2133172,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor